short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chamando os políticos pelos seus próprios nomes.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Mecanismator is a Chrome extension to replace the names of real politicians and corrupts in general with their fictional counterparts in Netflix and José Padilha's series The Mechanism.

Developed by LeTarrask
